snippet.title: #WarGames Teaser 2018 - New Interactive Series - Eko
snippet.description:
Shall we play a game? WarGames Teaser 2018, a New Interactive Series where you shape the story in #WarGames, coming soon from Eko, in partnership with MGM.

Created by Sam Barlow. Produced by m ss ng p eces.
